        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Marguerite's aching heart stood still.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "She felt, more than she heard, the men on the watch preparing for the fight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Her senses told her that each, with sword in hand, was crouching, ready for the spring.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Marguerite as she heard, felt that her very life was slipping away, as if when that voice drew nearer, when that singer became entrapped . . .",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Percy, my husband, for God's sake fly!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Armand! why don't you fire?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "The men had sprung to their feet, there was no need for further silence on their part; the very cliffs echoed the poor, heart broken woman's screams.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Into it, my men, and let no one escape from that hut alive!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "The door was partially open; one of the soldiers pushed it further, but within all was darkness, the charcoal fire only lighting with a dim, red light the furthest corner of the hut.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Quick, in every direction!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"But I ordered you just now, when the woman screamed, to rush in and let no one escape.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"You think?--You? . . .\" said Chauvelin, almost choking with fury, \"and you let them go . . .\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "We waited.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Hush! what was that?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "All three men listened attentively.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000048_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000048_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "He must have remained behind, and was even now hiding somewhere about the cliffs; the patrols were still about, he would still be sighted, no doubt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Bring the light in here!\" he commanded eagerly, as he once more entered the hut.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Pick that up,\" said Chauvelin to the sergeant, pointing to this white scrap, \"and bring it to me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Read it, sergeant,\" said the latter curtly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000061_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000061_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "They know it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000061_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000061_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Do not delay-and obey these instructions implicitly.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000063_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000063_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "But the latter had not waited an instant.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000065_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000065_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"There is a creek in a direct line from the 'Chat Gris'?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000066_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000066_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "I know it well.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000067_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000067_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"The Englishman is hoping to reach that creek.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000067_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000067_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "At any rate, there is a chance to get him yet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000069_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000069_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Within a few minutes their running footsteps had died away in the distance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000072_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000072_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "The cleverest woman in Europe, the elegant and fashionable Lady Blakeney, who had dazzled London society with her beauty, her wit and her extravagances, presented a very pathetic picture of tired out, suffering womanhood, which would have appealed to any, but the hard, vengeful heart of her baffled enemy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000077_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000077_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Ah! by the bye! where is the Jew?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000078_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000078_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Close by here, citoyen,\" said Desgas; \"I gagged him and tied his legs together as you commanded.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000080_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000080_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "His face in the silvery light of the moon looked positively ghastly with terror: his eyes were wide open and almost glassy, and his whole body was trembling, as if with ague, while a piteous wail escaped his bloodless lips.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000081_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000081_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Bring the cowardly brute here,\" commanded Chauvelin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000084_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000084_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Answer!\" he again commanded, as the Jew with trembling lips seemed too frightened to speak.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000085_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000085_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"Yes, your Honour,\" stammered the poor wretch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000088_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000088_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"There is no 'but.' I said, do you remember?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000090_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000090_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"What was the bargain?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000096_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000096_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "A low moan escaped from the Jew's trembling lips.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000097_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000097_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"But,\" added Chauvelin, with slow emphasis, \"if you deceived me in your promise, you were to have a sound beating, one that would teach you not to tell lies.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
