        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "Against a rock, on a hard bed of stone, lay the unconscious figure of Marguerite Blakeney, while some few paces further on, the unfortunate Jew was receiving on his broad back the blows of two stout leather belts, wielded by the stolid arms of two sturdy soldiers of the Republic.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7635_105409_000110_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7635/105409/7635_105409_000110_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7635",
        "content": "\"That will do,\" commanded Chauvelin, as the Jew's moans became more feeble, and the poor wretch seemed to have fainted away, \"we don't want to kill him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
